      "language": "python",
      "code": "```python\n# test_my_microservice.py\n\nimport pytest\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException\nfrom my_microservice import my_route\n\napp = FastAPI()\napp.include_router(my_route)\n\n@pytest.fixture\ndef app():\n    yield app.test_client()\n\ndef test_my_route(app):\n    response = app.post('/my-route', json={'key': 'value'})\n    assert response.status_code == 200\n    assert response.json() == {'result': 'Success'}```"
